name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Agent Harry Sieben
description: Harry Sieben is an expert in chemical and guerilla warfare. His own planet ravaged by wars and nuclear atrocities, he's made it his mission to learn as much as possible to prevent that from happening around the galaxy. Part scientist and warrior, he's the brain of most operations, creating tactical plans to suit any encounter and creates gadgets to assist the team. His own weapon has the ability to manipulate time in short durations to give him and his team an edge.
